title: 203: 2017 NFL Predictions
itunes:title: 203: 2017 NFL Predictions
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the season by predicting the 2017 MVP, Rookies of the Year and Super Bowl champion. The guys then break down the best sidekicks in the league. DJ and Bucky wrap the show by speaking to Jake Olsen, the inspiring long snapper from USC, before making this week’s college football picks.
